author: cms-l1t-offline
body:
This is the PR for tag l1t-tsg-v9.1 of L1T offline code.
With respect to l1t-tsg-v9.0 it contains new LUTs for new (Sept 2016) calibration constants and spike-killer. 
- At the last L1T meeting it was decided to go for this version of the code if the time permits.  It is still pending blessing of trigger performance.

This PR is not intended to be merged as is:
- [ ] status: pending rebasing once l1t-tsg-v9  is fully merged (i.e. #15823)
title: Pr81x l1t-tsg-v9.1 (NEW CALIBS) for Sept 2016 MC production
